{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/1.gif?t=1740331323\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Kirakira</strong> slimes are cute creatures that come in all shapes and colors, but they are also fragile, vulnerable to the perils of the world. Although legends say that slimes can combine and converge to become the <strong>Slime King</strong>, the strongest of all, able to face anything. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Could it be that the <strong>Kirakira Kingdom</strong> and its slimes are about to face a terrible threat? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HOW TO PLAY?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/2.gif?t=1740331323\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kirakira Slimes is a fun indie puzzle game in which you have to combine slimes strategically in an ever smaller space. Merge from the smallest to the Slime King, in order to get many points and top the highest score. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/slimecito1.gif?t=1740331323\" /> Combine two slimes of the same type to create a bigger one and increase your score. But be careful, the more slimes you have inside the box, the more chances you have to lose. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/3.gif?t=1740331323\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/slimecito2.gif?t=1740331323\" /> By combining slimes and scoring points, you will fill the<i> power up</i> bar. This gives you an additional ability. You decide when and how to use it most effectively. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/4.gif?t=1740331323\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/slimecito3.gif?t=1740331323\" /> There are <strong>11 types</strong> of playable slimes in total - combine, merge and power up your slimes in this indie puzzle, either playing alone or with friends in local versus mode! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/Comp-5.gif?t=1740331323\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Notes:</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>- While we are working to make the player experience as comfortable as possible, currently it's only possible to play the local multiplayer mode with 2 controllers. </i></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Fuuuuusion!!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2940660/fe6661592f61f8ebf280fc85a8817578a7e9f580.jpg"},{"name":"Slime Alchemist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2940660/8c39032b5945337d1e01bc6f5e21831320a9d477.jpg"},{"name":"Slime Hero","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2940660/5adc30934d0b42c8441660c103889e56cea7d00e.jpg"},{"name":"Union is strength","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2940660/992c1ed5db850394fd4666f97eb5d71b57c2c31c.jpg"},{"name":"Fusion King","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2940660/2aa3bf624c1fa4b8126d51d396dfe9ced29cf0d2.jpg"},{"name":"First Bright","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public